INSERT INTO `t_app_newscenter` VALUES ('605', 'http://mobile.163.com/13/1220/10/9GHGQEU0001117AG.html', '潮流耐用机皇 iPhone5s最新报价4350元', null, '', '<div id=\"endText\">\r\n  <p>\r\n    新发布的iphone5s有深空灰、金色以及银色三种颜色，机身由铝合金材质打造。苹果iPhone 5s最大的变化是A7的处理器，这是全球首款被用于智能手机上的ARM架构64位处理器，性能比iPhone 5的A6快2倍，是初代iPhone的40倍。苹果为iPhone 5s新增的指纹识别安全功能“Touch ID”更为这款新机增添了独具匠心的一面。苹果iPhone5S是一款苹果最新发布的，搭载最新A7处理器的智能手机。\r\n  </p>\r\n  <p class=\"f_center\">\r\n    <img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; BORDER-TOP: black 1px solid; CURSOR: pointer; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid\" id=\"content-first-img\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" src=\"http://img1.cache.netease.com/catchpic/F/F2/F2D9CA7D1CA82E78DDB01106B54BDE50.jpg\" align=\"no\"/>\r\n    <br/>\r\n    图：苹果iPhone 5S\r\n  </p>\r\n  <p>\r\n     苹果iPhone 5S仍旧坚持4英寸的屏幕，分辨率仍为1136x640像素。HOME键本身是块蓝宝石玻璃，按钮本身的不锈钢环可以检测手指接触，进而将用户的指纹透过HOME键传输到感应器。读取指纹的次数越多，指纹识别会越精准，并且Touch ID还支持多个指纹。用户的指纹信息全都加密存储在A7芯片里，不会被传输到苹果或iCloud，并且其它软件也无权访问。\r\n  </p>\r\n  <p class=\"f_center\">\r\n    <img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; BORDER-TOP: black 1px solid; CURSOR: pointer; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" src=\"http://img1.cache.netease.com/catchpic/3/3B/3B18C2724310D561597CB78B40E91833.jpg\" align=\"no\"/>\r\n    <br/>\r\n    图：苹果iPhone 5S\r\n  </p>\r\n  <p>\r\n     苹果iPhone 5S配备了一个全新的800万像素主摄像头，光圈f2.2，传感器面积比之前iPhone 5上的大了15%，单个有效像素的面积为1.5μm。机身背部的差异也有一些，iPhone5S背部采用了双LED闪光灯。总体来说，整机的成像效果是绝对不错的。\r\n  </p>\r\n  <p class=\"f_center\">\r\n    <img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; BORDER-TOP: black 1px solid; CURSOR: pointer; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" src=\"http://img1.cache.netease.com/catchpic/1/16/1674B513436D31E68B4D4871D4831FD9.jpg\" align=\"no\"/>\r\n     \r\n    <img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; BORDER-TOP: black 1px solid; CURSOR: pointer; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" src=\"http://img1.cache.netease.com/catchpic/A/AE/AE6F24B34066D47743DE29CFC4E4B538.jpg\" align=\"no\"/>\r\n  </p>\r\n  <p class=\"f_center\">\r\n    <img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; BORDER-TOP: black 1px solid; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" src=\"http://img1.cache.netease.com/catchpic/E/EE/EE253FD99667B1B14AE243C76CABE413.jpg\" align=\"no\"/>\r\n     \r\n    <img style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; BORDER-TOP: black 1px solid; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" src=\"http://img1.cache.netease.com/catchpic/3/3F/3FD84B23251FD8F8C3920BBC4691CB46.jpg\" align=\"no\"/>\r\n    <br/>\r\n    图：苹果iPhone 5S\r\n  </p>\r\n  <table style=\"WIDOWS: 2; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(162,199,225); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px auto; WIDTH: 648px; FONT: 14px/25px simsun; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); CLEAR: right; WORD-SPACING: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" class=\"param_table f_table\" cellspacing=\"1\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(208,208,208); PADDING-BOTTOM: 2.25pt; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(225,233,255); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(208,208,208); MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 2.25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 2.25pt; BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(208,208,208); FONT-SIZE: 12px; BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(208,208,208); PADDING-TOP: 2.25pt\" colspan=\"2\" height=\"30\" align=\"center\">\r\n          苹果iPhone 5S\r\n        </td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td style=\"BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(208,208,208); PADDING-BOTTOM: 2.25pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 18px; BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(208,208,208); MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 2.25pt; PADDING-RIGHT: 2.25pt; FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(208,208,208); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(208,208,208); PADDING-TOP: 2.25pt\" align=\"center\